read_surveys.Rd

Read Survey Files

Import surveys into a list. Add filename as a constant to each element of the list.

read_surveys(import_file_names, .f = "read_example_file")

Arguments

import_file_names

A vector of file names to import.
.f

A function to import the surveys with. Defaults to read_example_file.

Value

A list of the surveys. Each element of the list is a data frame. The respective file names are added to each data frame as a constant column filename.

Examples

import_file_names <- c(
'ZA7576_sample','ZA7562_sample','ZA7489_sample'
)
read_surveys (import_file_names, .f = 'read_example_file' )
